<plot>A mix between documentary and fiction that follows a group of kids living in very poor conditions in a 6-building complex in the middle of nowhere. Their parents work in a textile factory nearby. A group of film students teach them how to use a VHS camcorder and they start discussing and shooting their own movies.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?256225</url></doc>
